  "url": "https://www.evolutionq.com/products/basejumpski",
  "markdown": "[![evolutionQ](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/63ed3a30ffdcab681511d581_evolutionQ_logo.svg)](https://www.evolutionq.com/)\nProducts\n[ BasejumpSKI Symmetric key infrastructure solution that provides long-term security ](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/basejumpski)[ BasejumpQDN Ultra-secure key exchange for evolving quantum networks ](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/basejumpqdn)\nServices\n[ Quantum Risk Assessment Quantum-safe analysis for your risk management program ](https://www.evolutionq.com/services/quantum-risk-assessment)[ Quantum Briefing - Executive Workshop Executive briefing on quantum computing and threats by world-renowned experts ](https://www.evolutionq.com/services/quantum-safe-executive-workshop)[ Quantum Roadmap & Strategy Building a plan to address the quantum computing threat ](https://www.evolutionq.com/services/quantum-roadmap-strategy)\nResources\n[Resources](https://www.evolutionq.com/resources/resources)[Publications](https://www.evolutionq.com/resources/quantum-safe-publications)[FAQ](https://www.evolutionq.com/quantum-safe-cyber-security-faq)\nCompany\n[About](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/about)[Careers](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/quantum-safe-careers)[Events](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/events)[News](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/news)[Partner Program](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/partner-program)[Contact](https://www.evolutionq.com/contact)\n[Blog](https://www.evolutionq.com/blog)\n[evolutionQ Europe](https://evolutionq.eu/)[Contact Us](https://www.evolutionq.com/contact)\n# BasejumpSKI\u2122\nNavigate known and unknown threats with post-quantum security and resilience based on the multimodal key establishment protocol\n[Schedule a Meeting](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/schedule)[Whitepaper](https://frequency.evolutionq.com/kes-whitepaper)[Whitepaper](https://frequency.evolutionq.com/kes-whitepaper)[Technical paper](https://frequency.evolutionq.com/kes-technical)\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663accf995250af9f70d068e_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-min.jpg)\n### **Be ready for the new era of cryptography**\nEvolving cyber threats, malicious use of AI and advances in quantum computing all pose heightened risks for current cryptographic infrastructures.   \n  \nOrganizations are going to need both post-quantum public key infrastructures (PKI) and symmetric key infrastructures (SKI) to meet the challenge. The symmetric key infrastructures deliver an immediate, controlled way to achieve post-quantum key exchanges \u2014 enabling rapid post-quantum cryptography compliance today and laying the foundation for a resilient layered security posture going forward.  \n  \nBasejumpSKI\u2122, part of the Basejump\u2122 platform from evolutionQ, meets the challenge with a unique multi-modal approach that combines symmetric key infrastructure with post-quantum cryptography (PQC) for end-to-end key generation that\u2019s stronger and more resilient than the sum of its parts.\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad4c9d935ba3471c79472_evolutionQ-Multimodal-icon1.svg)\n###### Strong computational security\neven if all asymmetric cryptography used for key generation is broken.\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad4f49061ebf36fe73c0c_evolutionQ-Multimodal-icon2.svg)\n###### Forward secrecy\nto protect past communications even if long-term keys are eventually compromised.\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad4fddf3c50f74a656b93_evolutionQ-Multimodal-icon3.svg)\n###### Post-compromise security\nso that messages stay computationally secure even if long-term keys are compromised.\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad504777d6c76691a0a35_evolutionQ-Multimodal-icon4.svg)\n###### Identity theft protection\nfor confidentiality even if the infrastructure components are broken.\n### **Multiply your protection**\nDownload the datasheets to learn more about multimodal key establishment with BasejumpSKI\n[BasejumpSKI Datasheet](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/69b1efcf84672b9bff5e4cd0_00716D_eQ-BasejumpSKI_v04.pdf)[Basejump SEN-500 Datasheet](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/69b1efd020b449d224500605_00709D_eQ-BasejumpSEN500_v09.pdf)\n![evolutionQ Defense-in-Depth with Resilient-by-Design Multimodal](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0fd56230f2f220d2816_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img4-min.jpg)\n### **Cryptographic resilience leveraging symmetric key infrastructure**\nRelying on standards-based cryptographic methods, BasejumpSKI combines symmetric key, classical asymmetric key and post-quantum cryptography to establish end-to-end symmetric pre-shared keys (PSKs). These keys possess significantly stronger properties than other key management solutions, making them resilient to both classical and quantum computing attacks.\n### **Why BasejumpSKI**\nEnsuring the long-term, cost-effective protection of data in transit, BasejumpSKI:\n  * Provides post-quantum cryptographic resilience today while supporting long-term security, cryptographic agility and defense-in-depth against evolving threats.\n  * Integrates seamlessly into existing infrastructure without requiring the replacement of network equipment, making it both practical and cost-effective.\n  * Is future-adaptable, designed to evolve in response to emerging post-quantum and computational threats.\n\n\n![evolutionQ QKD networks](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0e9ad1a072f2f2f1cf5_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img1-min.jpg)\n![evolutionQ Long-Term Security \\(LTS\\)](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad17aca6e672a85b4bd83_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img2-min.jpg)\n### **Seamlessly integrate with existing infrastructure and quantum networks**\nBasejumpSKI is designed to seamlessly integrate into your current infrastructure, minimizing disruption while maximizing security. We work closely with you to develop a tailored solution that meets your specific requirements, optimizing security and efficiency for superior performance. We also provide ongoing support and maintenance.   \n  \nBasejumpSKI scales for widespread implementation and can be easily upgraded to work with quantum key exchange capabilities enabled by quantum networks, resolving their last-mile challenges by extending their range and increasing key availability.\n### Tried, true and real-world ready\nSchedule your BasejumpSKI demo today.\n[Book now!](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/schedule)\n[![evolutionQ](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/63ed3a30ffdcab681511d581_evolutionQ_logo.svg)](https://www.evolutionq.com/old-home)\nPRODUCTS\n[BasejumpQDN](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/basejumpqdn)[BasejumpSKI](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/basejumpski)[Technical Support](https://frequency.evolutionq.com/support-login)\nSERVICES\n[Quantum Risk Assessment](https://www.evolutionq.com/services/quantum-risk-assessment)[Quantum-Safe Executive Workshop](https://www.evolutionq.com/services/quantum-safe-executive-workshop)[Quantum Roadmap & Strategy](https://www.evolutionq.com/services/quantum-roadmap-strategy)\nRESOURCES\n[Resources](https://www.evolutionq.com/resources/resources)[Publications](https://www.evolutionq.com/resources/quantum-safe-publications)[FAQ](https://www.evolutionq.com/quantum-safe-cyber-security-faq)[Blog](https://www.evolutionq.com/blog)\nCOMPANY\n[About](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/about)[Careers](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/quantum-safe-careers)[Events](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/events)[News](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/news)[Partner Program](https://www.evolutionq.com/company/partner-program)[Contact](https://www.evolutionq.com/contact)\nSubscribe\nJoin our newsletter to stay up to date on features and releases.\n[Subscribe](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/basejumpski)\nBy subscribing you agree to our [Privacy Policy](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/basejumpski) and provide consent to receive updates from our company.\nThank you! Your submission has been received!\nOops! Something went wrong while submitting the form.\n\u00a9 2025 evolutionQ. All rights reserved.\n[Privacy Policy](https://www.evolutionq.com/legal/privacy-policy)[Disclosure Policy](https://www.evolutionq.com/legal/disclosure-policy)\n[Cookie Preferences](https://www.evolutionq.com/products/basejumpski)\n[![LinkedIn](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/64397268bacad8560a34f92a_linkedin.svg)](https://www.linkedin.com/company/evolutionq/)[![Twitter](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/6426526da75f4e45df4f421b_twitter.svg)](https://twitter.com/evolutionQinc)\nBasejump, BasejumpQDN and BasejumpSKI are trademarks of evolutionQ\n",
