dary margin-tiny w-button\" style=\"display: inline-block;\">Whitepaper</a><a href=\"https://frequency.evolutionq.com/kes-technical\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button secondary margin-tiny w-button\">Technical paper</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"header_background-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-overlay-layer3\"></div><div class=\"image-overlay-layer2\"></div><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663accf995250af9f70d068e_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-min.jpg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663accf995250af9f70d068e_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-min-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663accf995250af9f70d068e_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-min-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663accf995250af9f70d068e_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-min-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663accf995250af9f70d068e_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-min-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663accf995250af9f70d068e_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-min.jpg 1920w\" class=\"header_background\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\"><div data-poster-url=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663acc60330d80e57a869858_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-poster-00001.jpg\" data-video-urls=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663acc60330d80e57a869858_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-transcode.mp4,https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663acc60330d80e57a869858_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-transcode.webm\" data-autoplay=\"true\" data-loop=\"true\" data-wf-ignore=\"true\" class=\"header_video alt w-background-video w-background-video-atom\"><video id=\"98f8736c-ecd3-4bec-8803-9f5c51ae60ea-video\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" style=\"background-image:url(&quot;https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663acc60330d80e57a869858_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-poster-00001.jpg&quot;)\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" data-wf-ignore=\"true\" data-object-fit=\"cover\"><source src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663acc60330d80e57a869858_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-transcode.mp4\" data-wf-ignore=\"true\"><source src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663acc60330d80e57a869858_evolutionQ-Multimodal-bg-transcode.webm\" data-wf-ignore=\"true\"></video></div></div></header><section class=\"section_layout121\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large-2\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid layout121_component\"><div class=\"layout121_content-left\"><div id=\"w-node-d0ee7722-d7f1-703e-5b28-1c6e447dfcc5-c09e69d6\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h3><strong class=\"bold-text\">Be ready for the new era of cryptography</strong></h3></div><p>Evolving cyber threats, malicious use of AI and advances in quantum computing all pose heightened risks for current cryptographic infrastructures. <br><br>Organizations are going to need both post-quantum public key infrastructures (PKI) and symmetric key infrastructures (SKI) to meet the challenge. The symmetric key infrastructures deliver an immediate, controlled way to achieve post-quantum key exchanges \u2014 enabling rapid post-quantum cryptography compliance today and laying the foundation for a resilient layered security posture going forward.<br><br>BasejumpSKI\u2122, part of the Basejump\u2122 platform from evolutionQ, meets the challenge with a unique multi-modal approach that combines symmetric key infrastructure with post-quantum cryptography (PQC) for end-to-end key generation that\u2019s stronger and more resilient than the sum of its parts.</p></div></div><div class=\"layout121_content-right\"><div data-w-id=\"90120d01-9afe-cf23-4953-dfdecb4d8d96\" class=\"layout121_timeline-wrapper\"><div class=\"layout121_progress-bar-wrapper\"><div class=\"layout121_progress-bar\"></div></div><div data-w-id=\"90120d01-9afe-cf23-4953-dfdecb4d8d99\" class=\"w-layout-grid layout121_timeline-step\"><div class=\"layout121_timeline-left\"><div class=\"layout121_timeline-icon-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad4c9d935ba3471c79472_evolutionQ-Multimodal-icon1.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"icon-1x1-medium\"></div></div><div class=\"layout121_timeline-right\"><div class=\"layout121_text-wrapper\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h6>Strong computational security</h6></div><p>even if all asymmetric cryptography used for key generation is broken.</p></div></div></div><div data-w-id=\"90120d01-9afe-cf23-4953-dfdecb4d8da4\" class=\"w-layout-grid layout121_timeline-step\"><div class=\"layout121_timeline-left\"><div class=\"layout121_timeline-icon-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad4f49061ebf36fe73c0c_evolutionQ-Multimodal-icon2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"icon-1x1-medium\"></div></div><div class=\"layout121_timeline-right\"><div class=\"layout121_text-wrapper\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h6>Forward secrecy</h6></div><p>to protect past communications even if long-term keys are eventually compromised.</p></div></div></div><div data-w-id=\"90120d01-9afe-cf23-4953-dfdecb4d8daf\" class=\"w-layout-grid layout121_timeline-step\"><div class=\"layout121_timeline-left\"><div class=\"layout121_timeline-icon-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad4fddf3c50f74a656b93_evolutionQ-Multimodal-icon3.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"icon-1x1-medium\"></div></div><div class=\"layout121_timeline-right\"><div class=\"layout121_text-wrapper\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h6>Post-compromise security</h6></div><p>so that messages stay computationally secure even if long-term keys are compromised.</p></div></div></div><div data-w-id=\"90120d01-9afe-cf23-4953-dfdecb4d8dba\" class=\"w-layout-grid layout121_timeline-step\"><div class=\"layout121_timeline-left\"><div class=\"layout121_timeline-icon-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad504777d6c76691a0a35_evolutionQ-Multimodal-icon4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"icon-1x1-medium\"></div></div><div class=\"layout121_timeline-right\"><div class=\"layout121_text-wrapper\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h6>Identity theft protection</h6></div><p>for confidentiality even if the infrastructure components are broken.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_cta background-gradient\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-small\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"padding-vertical padding-medium\"><div class=\"text-align-center\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h3><strong>Multiply your protection</strong></h3></div><p>Download the datasheets to learn more about multimodal key establishment with BasejumpSKI</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group is-center\"><a href=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/69b1efcf84672b9bff5e4cd0_00716D_eQ-BasejumpSKI_v04.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button w-button\" data-lf-fd-inspected-3p1w24dr0mg8my5n=\"true\">BasejumpSKI Datasheet</a><a href=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/69b1efd020b449d224500605_00709D_eQ-BasejumpSEN500_v09.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button w-button\" data-lf-fd-inspected-3p1w24dr0mg8my5n=\"true\">Basejump SEN-500 Datasheet</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_content\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid grid_2_col_layout\"><img width=\"500\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 500px\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0fd56230f2f220d2816_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img4-min.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0fd56230f2f220d2816_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img4-min-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0fd56230f2f220d2816_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img4-min-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0fd56230f2f220d2816_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img4-min.jpg 850w\" alt=\"evolutionQ Defense-in-Depth with Resilient-by-Design Multimodal\" class=\"shadow-hard-blue\" height=\"376\" style=\"opacity: 0;\"><div id=\"w-node-_849ba81b-bb13-3417-55cd-aa9bd3411bb3-c09e69d6\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h3><strong>Cryptographic resilience leveraging symmetric key infrastructure</strong></h3></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Relying on standards-based cryptographic methods, BasejumpSKI combines symmetric key, classical asymmetric key and post-quantum cryptography to establish end-to-end symmetric pre-shared keys (PSKs). These keys possess significantly stronger properties than other key management solutions, making them resilient to both classical and quantum computing attacks.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_content\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><section class=\"section_content\"></section><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid grid_2_col_layout\"><div id=\"w-node-dae0b5b5-575b-69de-742d-4977cbca069c-c09e69d6\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h3><strong>Why BasejumpSKI</strong></h3></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Ensuring the long-term, cost-effective protection of data in transit, BasejumpSKI:</p><ul id=\"w-node-_63346e3f-624b-6e9b-25e7-ac78d700d5e7-c09e69d6\" role=\"list\"><li>Provides&nbsp;post-quantum cryptographic resilience today&nbsp;while supporting long-term security, cryptographic agility and defense-in-depth against evolving threats.</li><li>Integrates seamlessly into existing infrastructure&nbsp;without requiring the replacement of network equipment, making it both practical and cost-effective.</li><li>Is&nbsp;future-adaptable, designed to evolve in response to emerging post-quantum and computational threats.</li></ul></div><img width=\"500\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 500px\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0e9ad1a072f2f2f1cf5_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img1-min.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0e9ad1a072f2f2f1cf5_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img1-min-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0e9ad1a072f2f2f1cf5_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img1-min-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad0e9ad1a072f2f2f1cf5_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img1-min.jpg 850w\" alt=\"evolutionQ QKD networks\" class=\"shadow-hard-blue-right\" height=\"376\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_content\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><section class=\"section_content\"></section><div class=\"container-large\"></div><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid grid_2_col_layout\"><img width=\"500\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 500px\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad17aca6e672a85b4bd83_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img2-min.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad17aca6e672a85b4bd83_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img2-min-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad17aca6e672a85b4bd83_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img2-min-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/663ad17aca6e672a85b4bd83_evolutionQ-Multimodal-img2-min.jpg 850w\" alt=\"evolutionQ Long-Term Security (LTS)\" class=\"shadow-hard-blue\" height=\"376\" style=\"opacity: 0;\"><div id=\"w-node-_5d21948f-178c-32d4-7771-0b007b1d34da-c09e69d6\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h3><strong>Seamlessly integrate with existing infrastructure and quantum networks</strong></h3></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">BasejumpSKI is designed to seamlessly integrate into your current infrastructure, minimizing disruption while maximizing security. We work closely with you to develop a tailored solution that meets your specific requirements, optimizing security and efficiency for superior performance. We also provide ongoing support and maintenance. <br><br>BasejumpSKI scales for widespread implementation and can be easily upgraded to work with quantum key exchange capabilities enabled by quantum networks, resolving their last-mile challenges by extending their range and increasing key availability.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_cta background-gradient\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-small\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"padding-vertical padding-medium\"><div class=\"text-align-center\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h3>Tried, true and real-world ready</h3></div><p>Schedule your BasejumpSKI demo today.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group is-center\"><a href=\"/products/schedule\" class=\"button w-button\">Book now!</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"footer_component\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-top padding-xlarge\"><div class=\"padding-bottom padding-xxlarge\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid footer_top-wrapper\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid footer_left-wrapper\"><a href=\"/old-home\" id=\"w-node-_8fbbe76c-d328-efb3-fbea-41276d92584c-6d925845\" class=\"footer_logo-link w-nav-brand\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63e68dd55d1e0e13004da649/63ed3a30ffdcab681511d581_evolutionQ_logo.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"72\" alt=\"evolutionQ\"><